text:
on the way to the trojan wars, the hero philoctetes is abandoned by his fellow warriors because they cannot stand the stink of his infected foot. this myth can be used as a metaphor for what happens when compassion and empathy breaks down for men whose experience of sexual violation seems too terrible for those around them to bear. 
on december 1st in a cpd workshop, sarah van gogh will be in the lab to explore with us the issues related to working therapeutically with men who have experienced any form of sexual violation of abuse. through visualisation, drawing and group sharing we will look at the emotional, psychological and physical consequences, including sexual dysfunction, violent rage, and suicidal depression. all counsellors and therapists welcome. 
#stillpointspaceslondon #malevictims #abuse #metoo #depression #findatherapist #sarahvangogh #counsellors #therapists

text:
this hit me in all the feels today.

i remember fighting my wounds, shaming myself into deeper shame spirals for all that i knew and all that i couldn't undo. 
trauma is real and embodied. it travels with us. we carry it's truth in our bones and it echoes through our spirit.

do not beat yourself up for your scars. your wounds are real and your experiences are valid. 
none of your scars make you less. you are changed.

for the scars that linger below the surface, hidden from sight. i know you. i am you. 
the stones of abuse broke the surface of the water, sending out waves and residual ripple that changed the shoreline... and the stones piled up, forever changing the riverbed of my soul.

the wounds are real. the trauma is real.

i have been changed and shaped through all of this... and as i continued to flow and heal... as i began to stop fighting the wounds and honor them. i began to heal. ••• i believe you 
i hear you

i see you ••• i honor the battles you have survived. 
i contend for the healing that is beginning to rise.

you can do this hard, holy work.

@stacie.martin

#wildandholy #wildernessisholy #freerangepastor #ivegotnostringsonme #welcometothenewage #nosurrender #smashthebox #notsorry #riseup #resist #notakebacks #onedayatatime #youarenotthebossofme #believesurvivors #safespaces #metoo

text:
✨аукцион ✨
.
друзья, у меня для вас очередной аукцион. т.е. возможность приобрести качественную вещь из премиум тканей по привлекательной цене👍🏼
.
на кону комплект бортиков:
✔️4 бортика размером 60х30см (подойдут на круглую кроватку или на 3 стороны прямоугольной кроватки)
✔️материал: хлопковый сатин премиум класса, кружево, гипоаллергенный наполнитель: холлофайбер. текстильные завязки🎀
✔️расцветка как на фото (лаванда и шампань)
.
бортики не только украсят кроватку вашего малыша и сделают её уютной, но и обеспечат безопасность☝🏼
.
✅начальная ставка 1500₽;
✅шаг 100₽.
✅доставка почтой рф за счёт победителя 350₽.
✅аукцион завершается спустя сутки, после последнего повышения ставки, или спустя сутки, после публикации, в случае отсутствия ставок😉
✅победителем станет тот, кто оставит последний комментарий со своей ставкой.
.
‼️важно‼️если вы не готовы гарантировать выкуп лота в течение 2-х дней после завершения аукциона, прошу воздержаться от участия!

text:
pecunia non olet, il marcio sì.
prendiamo parola sulla vicenda che in questi giorni sta occupando social e giornali on line, riguardante un noto personaggio del mondo degli eventi musicali a genova: emanuele habanero podestà.  accusato da molte e molti di abusi, molestie, violenze e stalking, è diventato oggetto di dibattito pubblico solo dopo la rinuncia, motivata pubblicamente, di federico fiumani, a partecipare al supernova festival, avvisato, al pari di moltissimi/e altri/e colleghi/e, delle vicende violente che riguardano podestà. diciamo fin da subito che il nostro principale interesse riguarda le molte persone, principalmente donne, che, da anni e non da ieri, subiscono la violenza di questo personaggio. l'hanno detto, ma non sono state ascoltate. sappiamo benissimo cosa significhi raccontare di aver subito molestia, violenza, prevaricazione o stalking e non essere accolte quando lo si racconta, anzi essere sminuite, veder minimizzato quello che di orrendo ti è capitato e non essere credute oppure ignorate. se a questo si somma il potere che, in certi ambienti, ha il personaggio in questione, possiamo condividere la paura e la nausea di molte che hanno preferito tacere. anche perché chi ha parlato pubblicamente, come kants exhibition, mesi fa su fb è andata incontro all'oblio, oltre a conseguenze  legali per aver avuto il coraggio di dire la verità. non ci stupiamo di nulla e non pensiamo d'essere migliori di nessuno ma sappiamo quale sia la forza e l'importanza del #metoo e altrettanto siamo consapevoli che per non rimanere sole ad affrontare le conseguenze della propria presa di parola contro la violenza occorre il #wetoogether: la forza di autotutelarci restando le une al fianco delle altre. mettiamo da subito a disposizione tutti i nostri canali social e i nostri spazi di discussione e incontro per accogliere le testimonianze di tutte/i, che siano legate a questa vicenda o che siano legate ad altre situazioni tristemente simili (nonunadimenogenova@gmail.com).
#wetoogether #ioticredo #sorellanonseisola #24novembre

our voices and stories must be heard.

join us on november 22 at the assembly hall lawns for our clothes line project as we recognize the international day for the elimination of violence against women

text:
a woman and her three daughters. after dozens of appeals to the police went unanswered, this woman separated from her abusive ex-husband. still, she cannot count on local law enforcement to protect her rights. 
despite a 2012 law which raised the maximum prison sentence for “femicide,” the killing of a woman or girl on account of her gender, argentina is still struggling against widespread gender-based violence. thankfully, a grassroots, women-led movement known as ni una menos (not one [woman] less) has arisen in argentina, and is working to empower women and defend their human rights. in this series, karl mancini (@karlitomancini) shares some of his work on the inspiring women of ni una menos and their fight for justice. to learn more about both mancini's work and ni una menos, please follow the link in our bio. 
#opensociety #argentina #niunamenos #femicide #femicidio #conmisderechosnotemetas #16days #genderbasedviolence #metoo #hearmetoo

text:
a south korean cult leader was convicted on thursday and jailed for 15 years after he raped eight female followers - some of whom believed he was 'god'. pastor lee jaerock set up the manmin central church in guro, seoul, south korea, with just 12 followers in 1982. it grew to 130,000 members, most of whom revered the pastor and believed he was god. as a result, his victims were "unable to resist as they were subject to the accused's absolute religious authority", judge chung moon-sung told the seoul central district court.

but three of lee's followers went public earlier this year, as south korea was swept with a wave of #metoo accusations. the followers who exposed him described how he had summoned each of them to an apartment and raped them.
one of the women who had been a member of the church since childhood told south korean television:

i was unable to turn him down.

he was more than a king. he was god.

text_retweet:
regram from @feministerna -  ett slut på #metoo kräver trygga arbetsplatser 
#metoo har en gång för alla visat vilket enormt strukturellt problem sexuellt våld är. inte mins på jobbet, en plats där dom flesta av oss spenderar en stor del av vår tid. en viktig del i att få ett slut på detta är trygga anställningar, aktivt jämställdhetsarbete och införandet av dryga böter (i nivå med böter enligt gdpr-lagstiftning) för arbetsgivare som underlåter att agera vid sexuella trakasserier.

detta är 1 av 11 reformer som du kan skriva under i vårt upprop: https://med.feministisktinitiativ.se/ga-langre-metoo

text:
las víctimas del pastor lee jaerock, de 75 años, “eran incapaces de oponer resistencia, pues estaban sometidas a la autoridad religiosa absoluta del acusado”, subrayó el juez chung moon-sung ante el tribunal del distrito central de seúl.
la devoción religiosa puede ser muy fuerte en corea del sur, donde el 44% de los habitantes se declaran creyentes.
.
la mayoría de los fieles del país pertenecen a iglesias reconocidas, a menudo ricas y poderosas, frecuentadas por decenas de miles de fieles que no dudan en donar hasta el 10% de sus ingresos.
.
pero también hay muchas iglesias marginales, algunas de las cuales estuvieron implicadas en casos de malversación, coacción, “lavado de cerebro”, manipulación de fieles y otras actividades asociadas a prácticas sectarias.
.
lee jaerock fundó la iglesia de manmin, de inspiración protestante, en guro, un barrio pobre de seúl, en 1982. empezó con 12 fieles pero en la actualidad su iglesia afirma tener 130.000.
.
cuenta con una gran sede, un lujoso auditorio y su página web destaca el gran número de milagros que en ella se han obrado.
.
a raíz de las revelaciones del movimiento #metoo, que llegó también a corea del sur, tres fieles denunciaron este año al líder religioso, que las convocó en su casa y las forzó a tener relaciones sexuales.

text:
[ hoje, no balneário do meu novo ‘cantito’, vem alguém na minha direcção e pergunta:
“és a #miúda do insta, não és?!” • fico com vergonha, dou-lhe uma beijoca e ela fica meia atrapalhada e larga uma lágrima - não por me ver (obviamente) mas porque, tal como partilhou comigo, temos um desassossego e um passado (não tão passado quanto isso) menos feliz. • a anorexia também a apanhou a ela. diziam-me que quando a força lhe falta, é (não só mas também) ao meu perfil que recorre para ir buscar algum alento. • e aqui, já era eu quem ficara com lágrimas nos olhos.
isto dá que pensar! pois quando me dizem “não te devias expor tanto”, “não devias dizer/mostrar isto ou aquilo”...não o faço para me vitimizar ou, pelo contrário, porque acho que sou um graaande exemplo a seguir! faço-o sim porque criar empatia através da partilha de um texto, de uma fotografia, de um vídeo ajuda a desmistificar um problema que é real; é dar alguma “voz” a quem se revê numa situação de tamanho desespero como é um qualquer distúrbio alimentar. • “à minha miúda”, obrigada. ❤️ ]
.
.

.

text:
#25nov

las mujeres nos cuidamos entre nosotras
una y otra vez salíamos a las calles, a decir basta, a gritar que no queremos que ninguna más desaparezca bajo la sombra de la justicia, 
no es tiempo bajar la guardia y aunque la idea no es mantenernos preocupadas o alertas a que alguien nos pueda secuestrar, violar o matar, nada perdemos con mantenernos alerta dado las circunstancias que vivimos aún en nuestro país.

envia en tiempo real la ubicación de dónde es que te encuentras y asi podrán ayudarte.

#recuerda: los mecanismos y estrategias que usamos para cuidarnos entre nosotras pueden ayudar a muchas otras mujeres, #comparte si la información te parecio útil.

text:
för ett år sedan publicerades juristuppropet #medvilkenrätt som undertecknades av 5 964 kvinnor och icke-binära inom juristbranschen. följande krav ställdes: *vi kräver ett omedelbart slut på sexualiserande, marginaliserande, utnyttjande och nedvärderande av kvinnor i vår bransch. * vi kräver att de med maktpositioner i vår bransch – delägare på advokatbyråer, domstolschefer, chefer för myndigheter med flera – tar sitt ansvar. att de börjar agera med omsorg, slutar att blunda för övergrepp och ställer ansvariga till svars. * vi kräver att både kvinnor och män uppmuntras till att bryta tystnadskulturen på arbetsplatsen. den som vågar höja rösten ska inte straffas.
ett år senare förutsätts att ett gediget och evidensbaserat arbete förts för att säkerställa att ingen någonsin igen behöver vittna om missförhållanden på sin arbetsplats. det är nu hög tid för självrannsakan. är arbetsplatserna tryggare idag? hur har ni säkerställt att sexualiserande, marginaliserande, utnyttjande och nedvärderande av kvinnor i vår bransch upphört? att tystnadskulturen är bruten? hur skiljer sig dagens arbetsplats med den för ett år sedan? har ni arbetat förebyggande, uppmuntrat människor att höja rösten eller har ni straffat dem som vågar? vi som deltar i kampanjen #upptillbevis inom #medvilkenrätt gör det hand i hand, med en gemensam röst. vi vill se faktiska resultat: upp till bevis! #medvilkenrätt #upptillbevis #metoo  #juristupproret

text:
g r a t e fu l // happy thanksgiving
#advocate #idaho #thanksgiving 🦃 ——————————————————————
this thanksgiving, we have so many things to be grateful for. we would like to take some time to express what we’re thankful for at the family crisis center.

we are thankful for a supportive community, and for brave friends, family, and survivors who reach out to us. we are glad to serve and provide comfort and resources to anyone in need.
we are thankful for the movements that shine a light on domestic violence and aim to end it. we are thankful for those involved in these necessary movements. 
we are thankful for the individuals, groups, and businesses in our community that realize domestic violence is a serious issue and collaborate with us to support our mission. 
we are thankful for all the donors who give to us generously. we appreciate every single donation — each one helps the men, women, and children we serve who are affected by abuse.
we are thankful for our advocates who answer phones 24/7/365 and meet with clients regularly. compassion and commitment are at the core of this organization. 
we appreciate everyone who is a part of the fcc in one way or another, and we are thankful for the family crisis center community!
—————————————————————— #lifestyle #family #loveshouldnthurt #november #enddv #byui #dvfacts #dancing #entrepreneur #fall #design #wellness #marketing #friends #idaho #timesup #metoo #health #comedian #breakthesilence #idaho #graphicdesign #healthy #turkey #thanksgiving #autumn

text:
a woman raped in childhood is a work in progress. someone messed everything up and she has to start from scratch. that mess can last her whole life, everyday coming with its own work. 
i am that woman. i was raped in childhood. this account is where i’ll share my story, the way i see it. 🇫🇷 une femme violée dans l’enfance est un chantier permanent. quelqu’un a tout détruit et elle doit tout reconstruire. ce travail peut durer toute sa vie, chaque jour amenant son lot d’obstacles.

je suis cette femme. j’ai été violée alors que je n’étais qu’une enfant. sur ce compte, je partagerai mon histoire, comme je la vois.

#metoo #toutesensemble #feminist #feministe #womenrights #droitsdesfemmes #iambecoming #jemarchele24 #lensculturediscovery

text:
my heart is filled with gratitude as i dip my toes in #missionbeach today! 2018 has been a year for deep healing, immense growth, and letting myself fully #beher. 
owning my story and sharing it with the world has been terrifying at times. i'm blessed beyond words to be met with so much kindness and support.

thank you for loving me on this journey!

thank you for believing in my mission!

thank you for showing other #metoo survivors they too are lovable!

i love you!
